芒聰聙芒聰聙 What This Crucible Proves 芒聰聙芒聰聙
芒聙垄 Handler-local state IS filter memory (x芒聜聥芒聜聛, x芒聜聥芒聜聜, y芒聜聥芒聜聛, y芒聜聥芒聜聜)
芒聙垄 Biquad filter: real Audio EQ Cookbook coefficients
芒聙垄 Same tick() handler, different coeffs = lowpass/highpass
芒聙垄 Delay line: handler state as sample memory
芒聙垄 Nested handlers: Filter 芒聠聮 Delay in one chain
芒聙垄 RMS meter: multi-state accumulator (sum_sq, count)
芒聙垄 resume(y) with state = new_val: one line advances the filter

